{"tid":1993153,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"聯合國專員: 要求港府解釋「23條」如何不會違反《公民權利和政治權利國際公約》","createTime":"2020-04-28T14:40:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-10T02:28:23.000Z","uid":134071,"like":88,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"8b6f9d6773500e7f0bdf2a24963852d89485e845","tid":1993153,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T14:40:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/NathanLawKC/photos/a.645858435565493/2192265654258089/?type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FNathanLawKC%2Fphotos%2Fa.645858435565493%2F2192265654258089%2F%3Ftype%3D3&d=C0QxMr2ftqWfBh1dRblImAexVh8qxZHot2w31qr30Zg%3D&h=9e905deb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/NathanLawKC/photos/a.645858435565493/2192265654258089/?type=3</a><br />\n<br />\n羅冠聰 Nathan Law<br />\n23 分鐘 &middot; <br />\n【🇺🇳北京強推23條立法惹聯合國關注｜罕有六名專員去信港府 要求解釋如何不會濫捕濫告😡】<br />\n<br />\n政權、黑警一直將香港抗爭運動定性為「恐怖主義」，近來亦紛紛吹奏23條立法，<strong>導致聯合國人權事務委員會多名專員去信香港政府</strong>，批評相關「恐怖主義」定義太闊，容易濫用作打壓示威，有違國際人權標準。<br />\n<br />\n對於黑警近期用殖民惡法「煽動罪」拘捕抗爭者，專員亦批評，不少國家案例證明，「煽動罪」往往被用作箝制反對聲音，甚至用「國安」之名、或將示威者冠以「極端分子」，去清除國內維權人士，<strong>並要求港府解釋未來23條立法，如何不會違反《公民權利和政治權利國際公約》。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>今次係少有地有六名聯合國專員一齊聯署去信港府</strong>，質問港府會否濫用煽動罪名，可見北京近日連番動作，已經觸動國際社會神經，呢啲係黑警無論上幾多次聯合國、講幾多次大話都洗唔甩。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://spcommreports.ohchr.org/TMResultsBase/DownLoadPublicCommunicationFile?gId=25196&amp;fbclid=IwAR1v94kxsdHrt__50itKLTVpVf1ResxbkveYm8xehxmlxK9oEdVZ2sTzv98\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fspcommreports.ohchr.org%2FTMResultsBase%2FDownLoadPublicCommunicationFile%3FgId%3D25196%26fbclid%3DIwAR1v94kxsdHrt__50itKLTVpVf1ResxbkveYm8xehxmlxK9oEdVZ2sTzv98&d=C0QxMr2ftqWfBh1dRblImAexVh8qxZHot2w31qr30Zg%3D&h=a075b611\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://spcommreports.ohchr.org/TMResultsBase/DownLoadPublicCommunicationFile?gId=25196&amp;fbclid=IwAR1v94kxsdHrt__50itKLTVpVf1ResxbkveYm8xehxmlxK9oEdVZ2sTzv98</a>"},{"pid":"d843c839771ef600ca74991e1407cb1a202e295f","tid":1993153,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T14:40:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c354df2644c73bcfd69873ed9e3962c48164cf1","tid":1993153,"uid":31215,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T14:42:15.000Z","msg":"聯合國同WHO咁撚大分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2141e3148ddc47b63197a6a51855f40b6206034c","tid":1993153,"uid":311198,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"6c354df2644c73bcfd69873ed9e3962c48164cf1","tid":1993153,"uid":31215,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T14:42:15.000Z","msg":"聯合國同WHO咁撚大分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T14:45:33.000Z","msg":"唔使驚 中國而家入咗聯合國人權委員會 呢啲專員嘅任期一到會即刻換走佢哋 以後唔會再有人幫我哋 rip"},{"pid":"9875a50682f8062c82547a0a9b147fd10e94df22","tid":1993153,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T14:46:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bcc8067e6419150f7019a9889944c6925db2c35","tid":1993153,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T14:46:15.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"8345fcb249978b1284bebc27f4decbf844a74b6d","tid":1993153,"uid":168567,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"6c354df2644c73bcfd69873ed9e3962c48164cf1","tid":1993153,"uid":31215,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T14:42:15.000Z","msg":"聯合國同WHO咁撚大分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T14:46:29.000Z","msg":"最怕就係形式上做   9答完無左回事<br />\n跟住林奠記者會托托眼鏡講 &quot;根據聯合國專員...., 已向聯合國詳細解釋......「23條」絕無不妥....&quot;"},{"pid":"8072b1d938ffe82229348818b9eceb782dc230bd","tid":1993153,"uid":3553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020